comments: BEST PROF! Easily available to help you after hours. No textbook needed, only two papers to do and a final presentation. Extremely fun teacher/class. He also brings in people from the ADJ feild to come talk to the class about their jobs. Cool!
He is my favorite Prof in the ADJ/CRIM field. He is extremely helpful, funny, and knowledgable. He works with you to succeed. Best Prof EVER!
